<!-- ##### SECTION Title ##### -->
BReceiver

<!-- ##### SECTION Short_Description ##### -->
receives Blinkenlights packets

<!-- ##### SECTION Long_Description ##### -->
<para>
The #BReceiver object listens for Blinkenlights UDP packets. For each
frame that matches the receiver configuration, a user-defined callback
is called with the received packet.
</para>

